    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Deities, usually masculine, responsible for the creation of earth and the cosmos. Often coupled with earth mothers or mother goddesses, who may be responsible for human, animal, and plant fertility.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
